{"tid":2453981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美名校涉隱瞞華裔教授性侵中國學生 遭兩女索償逾千萬美元","createTime":"2021-03-20T00:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T04:44:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d800b6f769c5ff8110c8f8e704b2a5151034b6","tid":2453981,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T00:50:16.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）兩名中國留學生向伊利諾大學厄巴納香檳分校（UIUC）提出訴訟，指學校為了繼續吸引中國留學生，隱瞞華裔教授徐剛（Gary Gang Xu）涉嫌性侵女學生的惡行，並涉嫌販賣中國留學生、違反性暴力法等，向該校索償1,100多萬元（美元、下同）。原訴人律師韋基信（Alison Wilkinson）向《蘋果》表示，該校十分依賴來自中國留學生的收入，才對性侵行為袖手旁觀，而且加以隱瞞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210320/NL2BTYULYJHFJPSUAO2OMG4TA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210320%2FNL2BTYULYJHFJPSUAO2OMG4TA4%2F&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=02c37a66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210320%2FNL2BTYULYJHFJPSUAO2OMG4TA4%2F&h=a950b06f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210320/NL2BTYULYJHFJPSUAO2OMG4TA4/</a>"},{"pid":"5439465b539bc0e370a27f84eec4f10095236546","tid":2453981,"uid":132810,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T00:51:51.000Z","msg":"販賣中國留學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2b6db68da30757eb97cf1d3ed8643c58f140b1","tid":2453981,"uid":299187,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T00:53:08.000Z","msg":"係咪諗住靠上床拎Good grade?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d5c6cd687c818a5ec221431b8f8abf1446b26d","tid":2453981,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T00:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>涉嫌販賣中國留學